{"questionId":"e3bbde69","correctAnswer":"B","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Solve the system by substitution","content":"Substitute $y=9x+1$ into $8x+y=5$: $$8x+(9x+1)=5 \\Rightarrow 17x=4.$$"},{"title":"Find $x$","content":"So $x=\\tfrac{4}{17}$. That matches choice <strong>B</strong> — <strong>B</strong> is correct."}]}